msgstr "要更新一个作者，请从索引中检索该作者，应用更改，获取会话的索引计划，并调用 `addOrUpdate 方法` ，将作者实例作为参数传入。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To delete an Author by identifier, retrieve the session's indexing plan\n"
"and call `purge`, passing the author class and identifier in argument."
msgstr "要根据标识符删除一个作者，请检索该会话的索引计划，并调用 `purge 方法` ，将作者类和标识符作为参数传入。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
