#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
msgid "Configuring the application"
msgstr "配置该应用程序"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As usual, we can configure everything in the Quarkus configuration file, `application.properties`."
msgstr "和往常一样，我们可以在 Quarkus 的配置文件 `application.properties` 中配置所有内容。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Edit `src/main/resources/application.properties` and inject the following configuration:"
msgstr "编辑 `src/main/resources/application.properties` 文件，并注入以下配置："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We won't use SSL, so we disable it to have a more compact native executable."
msgstr "我们不会使用 SSL，因此我们禁用它，以获得更紧凑的本地可执行文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We need to tell Hibernate Search about the structure of our entities."
msgstr "我们需要向 Hibernate Search 说明实体的结构。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this application we consider an indexed entity (the author) is the root of a \"document\":\n"
"the author \"owns\" books it references through associations,\n"
"which *cannot* be updated independently of the author."
msgstr "在此应用中，我们将一个索引实体（作者）视为“文档”的根节点：作者通过关联“拥有”其引用的书籍，这些 *书籍无法* 独立于作者进行更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See <<quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-mapping-structure,`quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.mapping.structure`>> for other options and more details."
msgstr "有关其他选项和更多详细信息，请参阅 xref:quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-mapping-structure[quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.mapping.structure] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We need to tell Hibernate Search about the version of Elasticsearch we will use."
msgstr "我们需要向 Hibernate Search 告知我们将使用的 Elasticsearch 版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It is important because there are significant differences between Elasticsearch mapping syntax depending on the version.\n"
"Since the mapping is created at build time to reduce startup time, Hibernate Search cannot connect to the cluster to automatically detect the version.\n"
"Note that, for OpenSearch, you need to prefix the version with `opensearch:`; see <<opensearch>>."
msgstr "这一点很重要，因为不同版本的 Elasticsearch 映射语法存在显著差异。由于映射是在构建时创建的，以缩短启动时间，因此 Hibernate Search 无法连接到集群来自动检测版本。请注意，对于 OpenSearch，您需要在版本前添加前缀 `opensearch:` ；详情请参阅 <<opensearch>> 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This means that we wait for the entities to be searchable before considering a write complete.\n"
"On a production setup, the `write-sync` default will provide better performance.\n"
"Using `sync` is especially important when testing as you need the entities to be searchable immediately."
msgstr "这意味着，我们需等待实体可供搜索后，才将写入操作视为完成。在生产环境中，默认的 `“写入同步”` 模式将提供更好的性能。在测试时使用 `“同步”模式` 尤为重要，因为您需要实体能够立即被搜索到。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For development and tests, we rely on <<dev-services,Dev Services>>,\n"
"which means Quarkus will start an Elasticsearch cluster automatically.\n"
"In production mode, however,\n"
"we will want to start an Elasticsearch cluster manually,\n"
"which is why we provide Quarkus with this connection info in the `prod` profile (`%prod.` prefix)."
msgstr "在开发和测试阶段，我们依赖 xref:dev-services[Dev Services] ，这意味着 Quarkus 会自动启动一个 Elasticsearch 集群。但在生产环境中，我们需要手动启动 Elasticsearch 集群，因此我们在 `prod` 配置文件（ `%prod` 前缀）中向 Quarkus 提供了这些连接信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Because we rely on <<dev-services,Dev Services>>, the Elasticsearch schema\n"
"will automatically be dropped and re-created on each application startup\n"
"in tests and dev mode\n"
"(unless <<quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-schema-management-strategy,`quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy`>> is set explicitly)."
msgstr "由于我们依赖 xref:dev-services[Dev Services] ，因此在测试和开发模式下，每次应用程序启动时，Elasticsearch 模式都会被自动删除并重新创建（除非显式设置了 xref:quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-schema-management-strategy[quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy] ）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If for some reason you cannot use Dev Services,\n"
"you will have to set the following properties to get similar behavior:"
msgstr "如果由于某种原因无法使用 Dev Services，您需要设置以下属性以获得类似的行为："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See also <<quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-schema-management-strategy,`quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy`>>."
msgstr "另请参阅 xref:quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-schema-management-strategy[quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For more information about configuration of the Hibernate Search Standalone extension, refer to the <<configuration-reference,Configuration Reference>>."
msgstr "有关 Hibernate Search 独立扩展配置的更多信息，请参阅《 xref:configuration-reference[配置参考] 》。"

