#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Dev Services (Configuration Free Datastores)"
msgstr "开发服务（免配置数据存储）"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus supports a feature called xref:dev-services.adoc[Dev Services] that allows you to start various containers without any config."
msgstr "Quarkus 支持一项名为 xref:dev-services.adoc[“Dev Services”] 的功能，它允许您无需任何配置即可启动各种容器。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In the case of Elasticsearch this support extends to the default Elasticsearch connection.\n"
"What that means practically, is that if you have not configured `quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.elasticsearch.hosts`,\n"
"Quarkus will automatically start an Elasticsearch container when running tests or in xref:dev-mode-differences.adoc[dev mode],\n"
"and automatically configure the connection."
msgstr "对于 Elasticsearch，这种支持延伸到了默认的 Elasticsearch 连接。实际上，这意味着如果你没有配置 `quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.elasticsearch.hosts，` Quarkus 在运行测试或处于 xref:dev-mode-differences.adoc[开发模式] 时，会自动启动一个 Elasticsearch 容器，并自动配置连接。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When running the production version of the application, the Elasticsearch connection needs to be configured as normal,\n"
"so if you want to include a production database config in your `application.properties` and continue to use Dev Services\n"
"we recommend that you use the `%prod.` profile to define your Elasticsearch settings."
msgstr "在运行应用程序的生产环境版本时，需要按常规方式配置 Elasticsearch 连接；因此，如果您希望在 `application.properties` 中包含生产环境数据库配置并继续使用 Dev Services，我们建议您使用 `%prod.` 配置文件来定义 Elasticsearch 设置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Dev Services for Elasticsearch is currently unable to start multiple clusters concurrently, so it only works with the default backend of the default persistence unit: named persistence units or named backends won't be able to take advantage of Dev Services for Elasticsearch."
msgstr "Elasticsearch 开发服务目前无法同时启动多个集群，因此它仅支持默认持久化单元的默认后端：命名持久化单元或命名后端将无法利用 Elasticsearch 开发服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For more information you can read the xref:elasticsearch-dev-services.adoc[Dev Services for Elasticsearch guide]."
msgstr "如需了解更多信息，请参阅《 xref:elasticsearch-dev-services.adoc[Elasticsearch 开发服务》指南] 。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Programmatic mapping"
msgstr "程序化映射"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If, for some reason, adding Hibernate Search annotations to entities is not possible,\n"
"mapping can be applied programmatically instead.\n"
"Programmatic mapping is configured through the `ProgrammaticMappingConfigurationContext`\n"
"that is exposed via a mapping configurer (`HibernateOrmSearchMappingConfigurer`)."
msgstr "如果由于某种原因无法在实体上添加 Hibernate Search 注解，则可以通过编程方式进行映射。编程映射是通过 `ProgrammaticMappingConfigurationContext` 进行配置的，该上下文由映射配置器（ `HibernateOrmSearchMappingConfigurer` ）提供。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A mapping configurer (`StandalonePojoMappingConfigurer`) allows much more than just programmatic mapping capabilities.\n"
