msgstr "映射配置器（ `StandalonePojoMappingConfigurer` ）不仅具备程序化映射功能，还能 link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}#mapper-pojo-standalone-mapping-configurer[配置注解映射、桥接等更多] 功能。"

