#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Offline startup"
msgstr "离线启动"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, Hibernate Search sends a few requests to the Elasticsearch cluster on startup.\n"
"If the Elasticsearch cluster is not necessarily up and running when Hibernate Search starts,\n"
"this could cause a startup failure."
msgstr "默认情况下，Hibernate Search 在启动时会向 Elasticsearch 集群发送若干请求。如果 Hibernate Search 启动时 Elasticsearch 集群尚未运行，可能会导致启动失败。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To address this, you can configure Hibernate Search to not send any request on startup:"
msgstr "为了解决这个问题，您可以配置 Hibernate Search，使其在启动时不发送任何请求："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Disable Elasticsearch version checks on startup by setting the configuration property\n"
"<<quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch-version-check-enabled,`quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.elasticsearch.version-check.enabled`>>\n"
"to `false`."
msgstr "通过将配置属性 xref:quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch-version-check-enabled[quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.elasticsearch.version-check.enabled] 设置为 `false` ，禁用启动时的 Elasticsearch 版本检查。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Disable schema management on startup by setting the configuration property\n"
"<<quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-schema-management-strategy,`quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy`>>\n"
"to `none`."
msgstr "通过将配置属性 xref:quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-schema-management-strategy[quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy] 设置为 `none` ，禁用启动时的模式管理。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Of course, even with this configuration, Hibernate Search still won't be able to index anything or run search queries\n"
"until the Elasticsearch cluster becomes accessible."
msgstr "当然，即使采用这种配置，在 Elasticsearch 集群可访问之前，Hibernate Search 仍然无法进行索引或执行搜索查询。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you disable automatic schema creation by setting `quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy` to `none`,\n"
"you will have to create the schema manually at some point before your application starts persisting/updating entities\n"
"and executing search requests."
msgstr "如果您通过将 `quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.schema-management.strategy` 设置为 `none` 来禁用自动模式创建功能，那么在应用程序开始持久化/更新实体以及执行搜索请求之前，您必须在某个时间点手动创建模式。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"See link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}#schema-management-manager[this section of the reference documentation]\n"
"for more information."
msgstr "有关更多信息，请参阅 link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}#schema-management-manager[参考文档的这一部分] 。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Loading"
msgstr "正在加载"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As an alternative to using Elasticsearch as a primary datastore,\n"
"this extension can also be used to index entities coming from another datastore."
msgstr "除了将 Elasticsearch 用作主数据存储之外，该扩展还可以用于对来自其他数据存储的实体进行索引。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In such a scenario, you will need to set\n"
"<<quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-mapping-structure,`quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.mapping.structure`>>\n"
"to a value matching the structure of the primary datastore."
msgstr "在这种情况下，您需要将 xref:quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-mapping-structure[quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.mapping.structure] 设置为与主数据存储结构相匹配的值。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In order to do this, entities need to be loaded from that other datastore,\n"
"and such loading must be implemented explicitly."
msgstr "为此，需要从该其他数据存储中加载实体，且此类加载操作必须显式实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can refer to Hibernate Search's reference documentation for more information about configuring loading:"
msgstr "有关加载配置的更多信息，请参阅 Hibernate Search 的参考文档："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To load entities from an external datasource in order to reindex them,\n"
"see https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/stable/search/reference/en-US/html_single/#mapping-entitydefinition-loading-mass[Mass loading strategy]."
msgstr "要从外部数据源加载实体以便重新索引，请参阅 \" link:https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/stable/search/reference/en-US/html_single/#mapping-entitydefinition-loading-mass[批量加载策略] \"。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To load entities from an external datasource when returning search hits,\n"
"see https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/stable/search/reference/en-US/html_single/#mapping-entitydefinition-loading-selection[Selection loading strategy]."
msgstr "要在返回搜索结果时从外部数据源加载实体，请参阅 link:https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/stable/search/reference/en-US/html_single/#mapping-entitydefinition-loading-selection[选择加载策略] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In Quarkus, the entity loader mentioned in Hibernate Search's reference documentation\n"
"can be defined as a <<plugging-in-custom-components,CDI bean>>,\n"
"but will still need to be attached to particular entities using `@SearchEntity(loadingBinder = ...)`."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 中，Hibernate Search 参考文档中提到的实体加载器可以定义为 xref:plugging-in-custom-components[CDI Bean] ，但仍需使用 `@SearchEntity(loadingBinder = …​)` 将其与特定实体关联。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Management endpoint"
msgstr "管理端点"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hibernate Search's management endpoint is considered preview."
msgstr "Hibernate Search 的管理端点目前处于预览阶段。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In _preview_, backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed.\n"
"Specific improvements might require changing configuration or APIs, or even storage formats,\n"
"and plans to become _stable_ are under way.\n"
"Feedback is welcome on our https://groups.google.com/d/forum/quarkus-dev[mailing list]\n"
"or as issues in our https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[GitHub issue tracker]."
msgstr "在 _预览版中_ ，无法保证向后兼容性及在生态系统中的可用性。某些具体改进可能需要更改配置、API，甚至存储格式， _相关稳定版_ 开发计划正在推进中。欢迎通过我们的 link:https://groups.google.com/d/forum/quarkus-dev[邮件列表] 或在我们 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[GitHub 问题跟踪器] 中提交问题来提供反馈。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Hibernate Search extension provides an HTTP endpoint to reindex your data through the xref:./management-interface-reference.adoc[management interface].\n"
"By default, this endpoint is not available. It can be enabled through configuration properties as shown below."
msgstr "Hibernate Search 扩展提供了一个 HTTP 端点，用于通过 xref:./management-interface-reference.adoc[管理界面对] 数据进行重新索引。默认情况下，该端点不可用。可通过如下所示的配置属性将其启用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enable the xref:./management-interface-reference.adoc[management interface]."
msgstr "启用 xref:./management-interface-reference.adoc[管理接口] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enable Hibernate Search Standalone specific management endpoints."
msgstr "启用 Hibernate Search 独立版专用的管理端点。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Once the management endpoints are enabled, data can be re-indexed via `/q/hibernate-search/standalone/reindex`, where `/q` is the default management root path\n"
"and `/hibernate-search/standalone/` is the default Hibernate Search root management path.\n"
"It (`/hibernate-search/standalone/`) can be changed via configuration property as shown below."
msgstr "启用管理端点后，可通过 `/q/hibernate-search/standalone/reindex` 对数据进行重新索引，其中 `/q` 是默认的管理根路径， `/hibernate-search/standalone/` 是 Hibernate Search 的默认管理根路径。 该路径（ `/hibernate-search/standalone/` ）可通过配置属性进行修改，如下所示。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Use a custom `custom-root-path` path for Hibernate Search's management endpoint.\n"
"If the default management root path is used then the reindex path becomes `/q/custom-root-path/reindex`."
msgstr "为 Hibernate Search 的管理端点使用自定义路径 `custom-root-path` 。如果使用默认的管理根路径，则重新索引路径将变为 `/q/custom-root-path/reindex` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This endpoint accepts `POST` requests with `application/json` content type only.\n"
"All indexed entities will be re-indexed if an empty request body is submitted."
msgstr "该端点仅接受内容类型为 `application/json` 的 `POST` 请求。如果提交的请求正文为空，所有已索引的实体都将被重新索引。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In order to reindex an entity type,\n"
"it needs to be <<loading,configured for loading from an external source>>."
msgstr "要重新索引一个实体类型，需要将其 xref:loading[配置为从外部源加载数据] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Without that configuration, reindexing through the management endpoint (or through any other API)\n"
"will fail."
msgstr "如果没有该配置，通过管理端点（或通过任何其他 API）进行的重新索引操作将会失败。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If only a subset of entities must be re-indexed or\n"
"if there is a need to have a custom configuration of the underlying mass indexer\n"
"then this information can be passed through the request body as shown below."
msgstr "如果只需对部分实体进行重新索引，或者需要对底层批量索引器进行自定义配置，则可以如下所示将相关信息通过请求正文传递。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An array of entity names that should be re-indexed. If unspecified or empty, all entity types will be re-indexed."
msgstr "应重新索引的实体名称数组。如果未指定或为空，则将对所有实体类型进行重新索引。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sets the number of entity types to be indexed in parallel."
msgstr "设置要并行索引的实体类型数量。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The full list of possible filters and available mass indexer configurations is presented in the example below."
msgstr "下文示例中列出了所有可能的过滤器以及可用的批量索引器配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Filter object that allows to limit the scope of reindexing."
msgstr "一种过滤对象，可用于限制重新索引的范围。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An array of tenant ids, in case of multi-tenancy. If unspecified or empty, all tenants will be re-indexed."
msgstr "在多租户环境下，这是一个租户 ID 数组。如果未指定或为空，则将对所有租户重新建立索引。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Mass indexer configuration object."
msgstr "批量索引器配置对象。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sets the number of threads to be used to load the root entities."
msgstr "设置用于加载根实体的线程数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sets the batch size used to load the root entities."
msgstr "设置用于加载根实体的批处理大小。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sets the cache interaction mode for the data loading tasks."
msgstr "设置数据加载任务的缓存交互模式。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Whether each index is merged into a single segment after indexing."
msgstr "索引创建完成后，每个索引是否会被合并到一个分段中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Whether each index is merged into a single segment after the initial index purge, just before indexing."
msgstr "在初始索引清理之后、索引生成之前，是否将每个索引合并为一个分段。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Whether the indexes and their schema (if they exist) should be dropped and re-created before indexing."
msgstr "在建立索引之前，是否应先删除索引及其模式（如果存在），然后重新创建。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Whether all entities are removed from the indexes before indexing."
msgstr "在建立索引之前，是否会将所有实体从索引中移除。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Specifies the fetch size to be used when loading primary keys if objects to be indexed."
msgstr "指定在加载待索引对象的主键时使用的获取大小。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Specifies the timeout of transactions for loading ids and entities to be re-indexed."
msgstr "指定用于加载待重新索引的 ID 和实体的交易超时时间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Note all the properties in the JSON are optional, and only those that are needed should be used."
msgstr "请注意，JSON 中的所有属性均为可选，应仅使用所需的属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For more detailed information on mass indexer configuration see the\n"
"link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}#indexing-massindexer-parameters[corresponding section of the Hibernate Search reference documentation]."
msgstr "有关批量索引器配置的更多详细信息，请参阅 link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}#indexing-massindexer-parameters[Hibernate Search 参考文档中的相应章节] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Submitting the reindexing request will trigger indexing in the background. Mass indexing progress will appear in the application logs.\n"
"For testing purposes, it might be useful to know when the indexing finished. Adding `wait_for=finished` query parameter to the URL\n"
"will result in the management endpoint returning a chunked response that will report when the indexing starts and then when it is finished."
msgstr "提交重新索引请求将触发后台索引操作。 批量索引的进度将显示在应用程序日志中。出于测试目的，了解索引何时完成可能会很有帮助。在 URL 中添加 ``wait_for=finished`` 查询参数后，管理端点将返回分块响应，该响应会报告索引何时开始以及何时完成。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr "限制"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Hibernate Search Standalone extension cannot be used in the same application\n"
"as the xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc[Hibernate Search extension with Hibernate ORM]"
msgstr "Hibernate Search 独立扩展 xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc[无法与带 Hibernate ORM 的 Hibernate Search 扩展] 在同一个应用程序中使用"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/39517[#39517] to track progress."
msgstr "请参阅 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/39517[#39517] 以跟踪进展。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"AWS request signing is not available at the moment, unlike in the\n"
"xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc#aws-request-signing[Hibernate Search extension with Hibernate ORM]"
msgstr "xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc#aws-request-signing[与使用 Hibernate ORM 的 Hibernate Search 扩展] 不同，目前 AWS 请求签名功能不可用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/26991[#26991] to track progress."
msgstr "请参阅 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/26991[#26991] 以跟踪进展。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Optimistic concurrency control is not available at the moment."
msgstr "目前无法使用乐观并发控制。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HSEARCH-5105[HSEARCH-5105] to track progress."
msgstr "请参阅 link:https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HSEARCH-5105[HSEARCH-5105] 以跟踪进展。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Elasticsearch/OpenSearch do not support transactions,\n"
"so multi-document updates may fail partially and leave the index in an inconsistent state."
msgstr "Elasticsearch/OpenSearch 不支持事务，因此多文档更新可能会部分失败，并导致索引处于不一致状态。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This cannot be avoided like in the xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc[Hibernate Search extension with Hibernate ORM]\n"
"with xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc#coordination[coordination through outbox polling],\n"
"because that coordination requires Hibernate ORM and relies on the fact\n"
"that data is derived from that of a (transactional) relational database."
msgstr "这无法像 xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc[Hibernate Search 扩展] 那样 xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc#coordination[通过“发件箱轮询”进行协调] 来规避 xref:hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc[——该扩展基于 Hibernate ORM，] 因为这种协调机制需要依赖 Hibernate ORM，并且基于数据源自（事务性）关系型数据库这一事实。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Further reading"
msgstr "延伸阅读"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you are interested in learning more about Hibernate Search,\n"
"the Hibernate team publishes link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}[an extensive reference documentation],\n"
"as well as a page listing https://hibernate.org/search/more-resources/[other relevant resources]."
msgstr "如果您想进一步了解 Hibernate Search，Hibernate 团队发布 link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}[了一份详尽的参考文档，] 并提供了一个列出 link:https://hibernate.org/search/more-resources/[其他相关资源的] 页面。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "常见问题解答"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why Elasticsearch only?"
msgstr "为什么只用 Elasticsearch？"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hibernate Search supports both a Lucene backend and an Elasticsearch backend."
msgstr "Hibernate Search 同时支持 Lucene 和 Elasticsearch 后端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In the context of Quarkus and to build scalable applications, we thought the latter would make more sense.\n"
"Thus, we focused our efforts on it."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 的背景下，为了构建可扩展的应用程序，我们认为后者更为合理。因此，我们将精力集中在了此处。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We don't have plans to support the Lucene backend in Quarkus for now,\n"
"though there is an issue tracking progress on such an implementation in the Quarkiverse:\n"
"https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras/issues/180[quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras#180]."
msgstr "目前我们尚无计划在 Quarkus 中支持 Lucene 后端，不过 Quarkiverse 上有一个问题跟踪了该实现的进展： link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras/issues/180[quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras#180] 。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuration Reference for Hibernate Search Standalone"
msgstr "Hibernate Search 独立版配置参考"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<span class=\"icon\"><i class=\"fa fa-lock\" title=\"Fixed at build time\"></i></span> Configuration property fixed at build time - All other configuration properties are overridable at runtime <input type=\"search\" id=\"config-search-0\" placeholder=\"FILTER CONFIGURATION\" disabled>"
msgstr "<span class=\"icon\"><i class=\"fa fa-lock\" title=\"在构建时固定\"></i></span> 配置属性在构建时已固定 - 所有其他配置属性均可在运行时覆盖 <input type=\"search\" id=\"config-search-0\" placeholder=\"过滤配置\" disabled>"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "About bean references"
msgstr "关于 Bean 引用"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"First, be aware that referencing beans in configuration properties is optional and, in fact, discouraged:\n"
"you can achieve the same results by annotating your beans with `@SearchExtension`.\n"
"See <<plugging-in-custom-components,this section>> for more information."
msgstr "首先，请注意，在配置属性中引用 Bean 是可选的，实际上也不建议这样做：您可以通过在 Bean 上添加 `@SearchExtension` 注解来实现相同的效果。更多信息请参阅 xref:plugging-in-custom-components[本节] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you really do want to reference beans using a string value in configuration properties\n"
"know that string is parsed; here are the most common formats:"
msgstr "如果你确实想通过配置属性中的字符串值来引用 Bean，请注意该字符串会经过解析；以下是最常见的格式："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`bean:` followed by the name of a `@Named` CDI bean.\n"
"For example `bean:myBean`."
msgstr "`bean：` 后跟一个 `@Named` CDI Bean 的名称。例如 `bean:myBean` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`class:` followed by the fully-qualified name of a class, to be instantiated through CDI if it's a CDI bean,\n"
"or through its public, no-argument constructor otherwise.\n"
"For example `class:com.mycompany.MyClass`."
msgstr "`class：` 后跟类的完全限定名称，如果是 CDI Bean，则通过 CDI 进行实例化；否则，通过其无参的公共构造函数进行实例化。例如： `class:com.mycompany.MyClass` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An arbitrary string referencing a built-in implementation.\n"
"Available values are detailed in the documentation of each configuration property,\n"
"such as `async`/`read-sync`/`write-sync`/`sync` for\n"
"<<quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-indexing-plan-synchronization-strategy,`quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.indexing.plan.synchronization.strategy`>>."
msgstr "一个引用内置实现的任意字符串。可用值在各配置属性的文档中有所说明，例如 xref:quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch_quarkus-hibernate-search-standalone-indexing-plan-synchronization-strategy[quarkus.hibernate-search-standalone.indexing.plan.synchronization.strategy] 中的 `async/read-sync/write-sync/sync` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.15/guides/hibernate-search-standalone-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Other formats are also accepted, but are only useful for advanced use cases.\n"
"See link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}#configuration-bean-reference-parsing[this section of Hibernate Search's reference documentation]\n"
"for more information."
msgstr "也支持其他格式，但仅适用于高级用例。有关更多信息，请参阅 link:{hibernate-search-docs-url}#configuration-bean-reference-parsing[Hibernate Search 参考文档的这一部分] 。"
